t-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"8b9053e0-7f46-4310-a2a2-253505fb25b1\">IDR</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"161\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"fb137748-8c50-46bf-91e3-d8b72f453c7f\">4,000</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"466\"><p data-block-id=\"607ba616-36e5-420b-8af6-fbb60fd7ed58\">NPWP Validator (16-Digit Only)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"117\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"af7eeb7d-af82-4bfa-aaa3-e9b671e463ea\">IDR</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"161\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"fa3631fc-d887-4543-9ca5-9036193412b8\">400</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"466\"><p data-block-id=\"c350a822-209c-4f3a-b827-4605adfd902a\">KTP OCR</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"117\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"065a7959-35b4-4a7c-b0e5-371a76f0d2c9\">IDR</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"161\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"2aef0a39-b764-44b5-bd8b-1d285aded2ee\">500</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"466\"><p data-block-id=\"32bff858-3729-415f-a62b-08e5687384a0\">NPWP OCR</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"117\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"320955f0-77b7-4e1b-8fb3-e6f1a326925f\">IDR</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"161\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"27e0dba9-a09c-4052-90b2-7f0e37a590db\">700</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\" colwidth=\"122\"><p data-block-id=\"9f4760c6-8591-44c1-a606-4f1e16eeb155\">Philippines</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"466\"><p data-block-id=\"4b22bcc2-5c5d-4177-8aac-320ba2e70386\">Capture Link Verification (Includes OCR*, Document Forgery Check, Face Compare, Passive Liveness)</p><p data-block-id=\"1b172b98-480e-487c-9e33-c650bbbede10\">*Documents Supported: DL, SSS, UMID, TIN, Passport, Philsys</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"117\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"fefa3344-ec92-48f4-89d2-1d203b7b354d\">PHP</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"161\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"6f6ca564-ab3a-4e9e-bbe8-35b00d0dcbf8\">45</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"466\"><p data-block-id=\"80d22edb-bef9-4a47-b980-27ac3fc4ad80\">Business Document OCR</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"117\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"5b084ed1-4604-4554-bc8e-1ef03c311498\">PHP</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"161\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"b4917777-4c46-4a03-8738-acceb491b592\">30</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\" colwidth=\"122\"><p data-block-id=\"2505b59e-7e64-4956-ac56-f3bb2df6c05e\">Vietnam</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"466\"><p data-block-id=\"6ce2e097-2807-428d-8f5a-148000898a82\">Bank Name Validator (Version X.2)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"117\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"7e761568-21fb-449a-8f6c-efab26a3c06b\">VND</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"161\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"85029f9e-bb4c-4a55-b4ad-40cd5cf9395a\">0 *</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"466\"><p data-block-id=\"8e83996a-916c-407a-a97f-9b536df6caf5\">Bank Name Validator Details (Version X.1 - Raw Name Return)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"117\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"d68782db-2aea-4455-b725-ac9c812c9a8f\">VND</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"161\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"402cdc11-751b-4a12-b93a-30fe5aac21bd\">0 *</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><blockquote style=\"background:#ddf7ff;border-left:4px solid #006a8a;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"67a1a5b8-ea01-4f6e-9a8d-d65342e00e97\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"c1cb6908-62d7-4828-bb3a-98e62c396bbc\">How are customer charged?</p></div><p data-block-id=\"62a572a7-9c0f-4964-8893-bb21d38aa231\">The pricing above applies for each COMPLETED request, whether the result is a positive or a negative. Only FAILED request are not charged, which can be due to server errors on our side, or validation errors from the clients. Additionally, GET requests (for fetching results) are also free-of-charge.</p><p data-block-id=\"dc5329d2-e96b-44fd-b05f-8ee2d06013da\">All completed requests are tallied at the end of the month and is invoiced the following month, to be paid by transferring to a Virtual Account.</p></blockquote><p data-block-id=\"89d32ad2-36a4-45e3-a44f-c4be08f9d29a\">Tiered Pricing is also available upon request only for high-value clients. Please contact the relevant Product Manager for details.</p><p data-block-id=\"a078bb8a-8a59-4c79-9a4d-7680796bfb8f\">*VND Pricing: Bank NV is free for local-Vietnamese merchants because it’s expected to be a free service in Vietnam. If the merchant is foreign to VN, or uses both ID and VN Bank validators, then we should default to the IDR pricing.</p><h3 data-block-id=\"bc5f488a-c15e-4f5f-8a15-fc264f34f632\">Service Agreements (Commercials)</h3><ul data-block-id=\"a468476d-b254-4bf6-b9f4-8c0075fc8f76\"><li data-block-id=\"b8d94da1-1cab-47a2-974e-a5fa87d184d6\"><p data-block-id=\"941e4fdf-c9ee-4c6a-aacb-8bbe240a2157\">Global, ID and VN Products: Iluma SA (SpotDraft)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"4c1f5bd9-3bf8-4b3a-b398-bdde50fc3d57\"><p data-block-id=\"6055ca7e-faa8-44e8-94b3-b6f26f54a00a\">Global &amp; PH Products: Xendit Philippines Addendum (Interco with Iluma)</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"d7a12db2-7d27-4c64-a1bb-f39bb62dfedf\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Pricing","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Harga","Slug":"pricing","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id]