><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"466\"><p data-block-id=\"f76e3493-68b5-422f-8bcc-45a9b4bbb96a\">Individual Authentication (KTP Data)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"117\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"8b9053e0-7f46-4310-a2a2-253505fb25b1\">IDR</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"161\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"fb137748-8c50-46bf-91e3-d8b72f453c7f\">4,000</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"466\"><p data-block-id=\"607ba616-36e5-420b-8af6-fbb60fd7ed58\">NPWP Validator (16-Digit Only)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"117\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"af7eeb7d-af82-4bfa-aaa3-e9b671e463ea\">IDR</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"161\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"fa3631fc-d887-4543-9ca5-9036193412b8\">400</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"466\"><p data-block-id=\"c350a822-209c-4f3a-b827-4605adfd902a\">KTP OCR</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"117\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"065a7959-35b4-4a7c-b0e5-371a76f0d2c9\">IDR</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"161\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"2aef0a39-b764-44b5-bd8b-1d285aded2ee\">500</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"466\"><p data-block-id=\"32bff858-3729-415f-a62b-08e5687384a0\">NPWP OCR</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"117\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"320955f0-77b7-4e1b-8fb3-e6f1a326925f\">IDR</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"161\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"27e0dba9-a09c-4052-90b2-7f0e37a590db\">700</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\" colwidth=\"122\"><p data-block-id=\"9f4760c6-8591-44c1-a606-4f1e16eeb155\">Filipina</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"466\"><p data-block-id=\"4b22bcc2-5c5d-4177-8aac-320ba2e70386\">Capture Link Verification (Termasuk OCR*, Pemeriksaan Pemalsuan Dokumen, Perbandingan Wajah, Passive Liveness)</p><p data-block-id=\"1b172b98-480e-487c-9e33-c650bbbede10\">*Dokumen yang Didukung: DL, SSS, UMID, TIN, Passport, Philsys</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"117\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"fefa3344-ec92-48f4-89d2-1d203b7b354d\">PHP</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"161\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"6f6ca564-ab3a-4e9e-bbe8-35b00d0dcbf8\">45</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"466\"><p data-block-id=\"80d22edb-bef9-4a47-b980-27ac3fc4ad80\">Business Document OCR</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"117\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"5b084ed1-4604-4554-bc8e-1ef03c311498\">PHP</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"161\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"b4917777-4c46-4a03-8738-acceb491b592\">30</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\" colwidth=\"122\"><p data-block-id=\"2505b59e-7e64-4956-ac56-f3bb2df6c05e\">Vietnam</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"466\"><p data-block-id=\"6ce2e097-2807-428d-8f5a-148000898a82\">Bank Name Validator (Version X.2)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"117\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"7e761568-21fb-449a-8f6c-efab26a3c06b\">VND</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"161\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"85029f9e-bb4c-4a55-b4ad-40cd5cf9395a\">0 *</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"466\"><p data-block-id=\"8e83996a-916c-407a-a97f-9b536df6caf5\">Bank Name Validator Details (Version X.1 - Raw Name Return)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"117\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"d68782db-2aea-4455-b725-ac9c812c9a8f\">VND</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"161\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"402cdc11-751b-4a12-b93a-30fe5aac21bd\">0 *</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><blockquote style=\"background:#ddf7ff;border-left:4px solid #006a8a;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"67a1a5b8-ea01-4f6e-9a8d-d65342e00e97\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"c1cb6908-62d7-4828-bb3a-98e62c396bbc\">Bagaimana pelanggan dikenakan biaya?</p></div><p data-block-id=\"62a572a7-9c0f-4964-8893-bb21d38aa231\">Harga di atas berlaku untuk setiap permintaan yang SELESAI, baik hasilnya positif maupun negatif. Hanya permintaan yang GAGAL yang tidak dikenakan biaya, yang dapat disebabkan oleh kesalahan server di pihak kami, atau kesalahan validasi dari klien. Selain itu, permintaan GET (untuk mengambil hasil) juga tidak dikenakan biaya.</p><p data-block-id=\"dc5329d2-e96b-44fd-b05f-8ee2d06013da\">Semua permintaan yang selesai akan dihitung pada akhir bulan dan ditagihkan pada bulan berikutnya, untuk dibayar dengan mentransfer ke Virtual Account.</p></blockquote><p data-block-id=\"89d32ad2-36a4-45e3-a44f-c4be08f9d29a\">Harga Berjenjang (Tiered Pricing) juga tersedia berdasarkan permintaan hanya untuk klien bernilai tinggi. Silakan hubungi Manajer Produk yang relevan untuk detailnya.</p><p data-block-id=\"a078bb8a-8a59-4c79-9a4d-7680796bfb8f\">*Harga VND: Bank NV gratis untuk merchant lokal Vietnam karena diharapkan menjadi layanan gratis di Vietnam. Jika merchant tersebut adalah merchant asing di VN, atau menggunakan validator Bank ID dan VN, maka kami akan menggunakan harga IDR secara default.</p><h3 data-block-id=\"bc5f488a-c15e-4f5f-8a15-fc264f34f632\">Perjanjian Layanan (Komersial)</h3><ul data-block-id=\"a468476d-b254-4bf6-b9f4-8c0075fc8f76\"><li data-block-id=\"b8d94da1-1cab-47a2-974e-a5fa87d184d6\"><p data-block-id=\"941e4fdf-c9ee-4c6a-aacb-8bbe240a2157\">Produk Global, ID, dan VN: Iluma SA (SpotDraft)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"4c1f5bd9-3bf8-4b3a-b398-bdde50fc3d57\"><p data-block-id=\"6055ca7e-faa8-44e8-94b3-b6f26f54a00a\">Produk Global &amp; PH: Adendum Xendit Filipina (Interco dengan Iluma)</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"d7a12db2-7d27-4c64-a1bb-f39bb62dfedf\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Harga","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"ราคา","Slug":"pricing","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"772e0744-dbd5-4271-81f1-dc710d5209d3\">นี่คืออัตราค่าบริการล่าสุดสำหรับผลิตภัณฑ์ Verification ทั้งหมดที่ให้บริการผ่าน Iluma</p><p data-block-id=\"0174df69-c122-4986-ba5b-1c54be3f8f2d\">เอกสารประกอบ API: <a href=\"https://docs.iluma.ai/#introduction\" translate=\"no\">https://docs.iluma.ai/#introduction</a></p><h2 data-block-id=\"85d72e2e-8e64-4690-9ed5-4f21dbd81ce3\">คู่มือราคาสำหรับผลิตภัณฑ์ Verification</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"866\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:866px;width:866px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:122px;\"><col style=\"width:466px;\"><col style=\"width:117px;\"><col style=\"width:161px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"122\"><p data-block-id=\"1e090362-6844-4645-8c08-c4f21260efc5\">ภูมิภาค</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"466\"><p data-block-id=\"d0f0b2a7-9f1f-4b2f-bd8d-d275e444de32\">Product</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"117\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"f69d97f9-f1b1-405b-9a25-b8fa4cad2fdd\">สกุลเงิน</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"161\" style=\"text-align:right;\"><p data-block-id=\"dd5b346b-e21c-443e-a2c0-ef0815072e34\">ราคาต่อ Request</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"5\" colwidth=\"122\"><p data-block-id=\"e4c8a394-25f3-49